  "texts": [
    "Consequently, the combined impact of training and operation for ChatGPT amounts to approximately 2.2 g CO2e per query.",
    "For BLOOM, assuming a similar level of usage and frequency of retraining as for ChatGPT, the per-query impact of training is 0.10 g CO2e, while the per-query operational cost is 1.47 g. This results in a total emission of 1.6 g per query for BLOOM.",
    "We also calculated the embodied energy of the chips used to train the model and of the server used to deliver the query, and the end-of-life recycling of those devices, but all of these factors were 2-5 orders of magnitude smaller than the training and per-query emissions.",
    "The embodied energy footprint of an A100 GPU is 150 kg CO2e 12.",
    "The energy footprint for recycling an equivalent device is 1 kg CO2e 19."
  ],
